strings: <voice_0x01001D16><se_high>media princess: Wouldn't it be strange that Marcelo would come to the rescue?
<voice_0x01001D17><se_high>media princess: Having met him, I can say that I know very little about this man.
<voice_0x01001D18><se_high>media princess: Go ahead and embrace your weakness!
<voice_0x01001D19><se_high>media princess: I haven't written this yet but...
<voice_0x01001D1A><se_high>media princess: When I got to the vacant lot, I saw her behind me.
<voice_0x01001D1B><se_high>media princess: On the way he stopped and bowed down.
<voice_0x01001D1C><se_high>media princess: I'm not sure, but it seems that Neo's wounds have not healed yet.
<voice_0x01001D1D><se_high>media princess: I wonder why he was following us like that.
<voice_0x01001D1E><se_high>media princess: Maybe he was worried about Angel... Maybe everything he said on Guybee Island was just an excuse?
<voice_0x01001D1F><se_high>media princess: I know they've been through a lot, but I hope they find peace with each other.
<voice_0x01001D20><se_high>media princess: Because they are the only family in the world.
